textBeforeTable: Index of Scoring Results Scored with WSTIMS For Windows Version 2.0.1.2 3/15/2014 Master Scorebook Results as of April 7, 2014 20:04 14U045C KATY COLLEGIATE 14U045C KATY COLLEGIATE     Congratulations to all skiers for a great tournament.  A special thanks to our tournament officials, parents, alumni, and the Katy Homeowner's Association whom made this tournament possible.  For a full score book, please click Read More...   The South Central Region hosted its second tournament at Lakes of Katy in Houston Texas hosted by Lakes of Katy Homeowners Association.  The Aggies of Texas A&M University won the tournament's combined teams title, followed by Texas State and University of Texas.   South Central Katy Collegiate National Collegiate Water Ski Association Katy Collegiate Results Home Results Teams Log In Midwest Alumni Regionals 2015 Alumni Board of Directors International Activities Committee Athlete
